    The sqrcaps bundle provides packages and fonts for a script based on
the Square Capitals manuscript bookhand used from the 1st century AD.
The script consists of capital letters and digits, with some appropriate
period punctuation marks; both normal and bold versions are supplied.
The bundle is one of a series for bookhand scripts.

Changes in version 1.1 (2005/03/31)
o Fonts supplied as Postscript Type1 instead of MetaFont

Changes in version 1.0 (2002/12/30)
o First public release

